title: What are the most high output passive pickups for metal? - Quora

response.answer_text: There is no one definitive answer as there is no singular way to measure the output of a pickup. DC Resistance is not an absolute measure of output. I should also add… high output does not mean great sound. Some high output passives: Dimarzio X2N Duncan Invader Duncan Double Slug Duncan Hot Rails Gibson Dirty Fingers Kent Armstrong Motherbucker
